e is clean,” “the staff is friendly”).\n- **Coding:** Use an inductive coding approach to categorize responses into meaningful themes.\n- **Triangulation:** Cross-check qualitative findings with quantitative data to validate or contrast results.\n\n#### **4.3. Mixed-Methods Integration**\n\n- Use **convergent parallel design**","logprobs":null,"finish_reason":"length","matched_stop":null}],"usage":{"prompt_tokens":1,"total_tokens":513,"completion_tokens":512,"prompt_tokens_details":null,"reasoning_tokens":0},"metadata":{"weight_version":"default"}}'
